        <updateDate>2020-10-28T17:53:58Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Refusal to Accept Losses or Liability In Every Situation Act or RALLIES Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes unenforceable any liability waiver pertaining to contracting COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) at an indoor gathering of more than 1,000 people in a locality experiencing a 14-day increase in the number of COVID-19 cases.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
